 <br /><br />
 <h2><a name="fontsize">Font size</a></h2>
 
 The font size on these pages is set to "100%", which instructs the browser to use your default settings.
 
 To reset your default font:
 <table><tr><td>
 <ul>
 <li>Internet Explorer: size click on "view" in the menu bar (or enter <alt>-v on the keyboard), then select "font size".
 &lt;/li&gt;
 <li>Firefox: Select "edit" from the menu bar, then "preferences". In the pop-up, select "content": the "fonts &amp; colours" section should be half way down the pop-up box.
 &lt;/ul&gt;
 &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
 
 
 
 
</li></alt></li></ul></td></tr></table></div>
